contentrichtext.text: {{Use dmy dates|date=February 2013}} '''USS ''Keokuk''''' may refer to: *{{USS|Keokuk|1862}}, was an [[ironclad steamer]] launched 6 December 1862 and was sunk by [[Confederate States of America|Confederate]] forces on 8 April 1863 *{{USS|Keokuk|CMC-6}}, was acquired by the [[US Navy]] 28 July 1941 and sold 7 March 1947 *{{USS|Keokuk|YTB-771}}, is a large harbor tugboat launched 21 May 1964 and currently in active service {{Shipindex}} {{Italic title prefixed|3}} {{DEFAULTSORT:Keokuk}} [[Category:United States Navy ship names]]
